item.title: CVE-2019-18373|2024-08-05T01:54:14.199Z -- symantec -- norton%20applock
item.description: Norton App Lock, prior to 1.4.0.503, may be susceptible to a bypass exploit. In this type of circumstance, the exploit can allow the user to circumvent the app to prevent it from locking other apps on the device, thereby allowing the individual to gain access.
